  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Solar for Internally Displaced Persons Camps</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Our project addresses the problem of lack of clean energy for lightening in Internally Displaced Persons Camps and communities in North East Nigeria. The insurgency in North East Nigeria caused  by the terrorist group Boko Haram have displaced over 2 million people who are taking shelter in different internally displaced persons camp in different parts of the country. Nearly all the camps are without electricity. Our project is to provide electricity at the camps using Solar Energy</narrative>
  </description>
